-- Tottenham Beats Aston Villa, Liverpool Draws in Premier League
-- B y   P e t e r - J o s e p h   H e g a r t y
-- 2012-10-07T15:55:36Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-07/tottenham-beats-aston-villa-liverpool-draws-in-premier-league.html
Tottenham beat Aston Villa 2-0 and
Liverpool drew 0-0 with Stoke today in English soccer’s Premier
League.  Steven Caulker and  Aaron Lennon  scored for Tottenham at
White Hart Lane.  Earlier today, Jose Fonte scored twice as Southampton tied
2-2 against Fulham to climb out of the relegation positions.  In today’s other match, Newcastle hosts  Manchester United .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
